body_html:
Anyway, @Androbin I noticed you're using tf.contrib.signal.stft here -- note that tf.lite doesn't support complex numbers at the moment so once you get past this bug you'll still have issues.

I'm in the process of adding complex64 and RFFT/IRFFT support to tf.lite and I'll be making sure tf.contrib.signal.stft works in the process. complex64 is currently out for code review, so I'm hopeful this can make it into the next TensorFlow release.
